-- MOVES-Hargreave Hale hires David Clinkard from Brewin Dolphin
-- 
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 06:25AM EDT
-- None



Oct 16 (Reuters) - UK-based asset manager Hargreave Hale Ltd said it appointed David Clinkard as investment director to its investment management team.

The company, which also provides brokerage services, said Clinkard will be based at its newly opened York office.